Rory McIlroy will start his bid for a second straight major victory at 1.45 pm on Thursday when he tees it up for the 96th US PGA Championship .

Open winner McIlroy will be joined by Masters champion Bubba Watson and Martin Kaymer , who won the US Open earlier in the summer , for the first two rounds at Valhalla .

Northern Irishman McIlroy , winner of this event in 2012 , arrives in Kentucky as the bookies ' favourite after reclaiming top spot in the world rankings with his win at the WGC Bridgestone Invitational last weekend .

