The European challenge is strong at the scene of America 's last Ryder Cup triumph - back in 2008 - with Justin Rose , Sergio Garcia and Henrik Stenson all tipped for a big week .

Englishman Rose is alongside Louis Oosthuizen and Matt Kuchar while Garcia , runner-up to McIlroy at Hoylake and Bridgestone in his last two starts , plays with Steve Stricker and Tom Watson .

Swedish hopeful Stenson has Kenny Perry and Ryan Moore for company .

